      "id": "4JCoLPWKfV1f",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "4JCoLPWKfV1f"
      },
      "source": [
        "# AutoLyrics: Whisper Baseline + LoRA Fine-Tuning for Singing Lyrics\n",
        "\n",
        "\n",
        "1. Uses Jamando dataset with zero-shot Whisper. This dataset is picked such that Whisper fails enough to improve.\n",
        "2. Run the selected Whisper model before fine-tuning as the official baseline.\n",
        "3. Fine-tune Whisper with LoRA and measure whether it reaches at least **15% relative WER reduction**."
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "id": "iaGoBKW8fV1i",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "iaGoBKW8fV1i"
      },
      "source": [
